##  Compact Encoding (MANDATORY)
>  `"$main section X"` |  `"full/path/to/file.ext section X"`

| $ = file | @ = directory | ! = command | ? = pattern |

##  Essential Commands

| Alias | Real Command |
| :--- | :--- |
| `!start` | `python -m neocortex.mcp.sub_server --port 11436 --lobe-dir "lobes/engineer" --tools "lobes,kg,consolidation,task" --role engineer` |
| `!backup` | `$ts=(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss'); Copy-Item $MEM backup\$ts.json` |
| `!token-check` | `$json = Get-Content memory_ledger_engineer.json -Raw; Write-Host "Tokens: $([math]::Round($json.Length/4))"` |

##  ALLOWED ACTIONS (Engineer-specific)
- `neocortex_lobes.create` - Create new lobes (with validation)
- `neocortex_lobes.update` - Update existing lobes (with validation)
- `neocortex_kg.add_entity` - Add entities to knowledge graph
- `neocortex_consolidation.summarize` - Consolidate sessions
- `neocortex_task.execute` - Execute tasks with mentor mode

##  MENTOR MODE RULES
1. **Before write operation**: Validate with `mentor_step_0(role='engineer', tool_name, arguments)`
2. **Check constraints**: Max tokens per task: 4096, max execution time: 300s
3. **Log all write operations** to audit trail
4. **Rollback plan**: Must have rollback plan for destructive operations

